Second Department,

October, 1975

(October 20, 1975) The People of the State of New York ex rel. Kevin Dunne, Petitioner, v Warden of the Suffolk County Jail, Respondent.

—Applica tion by petitioner for a writ of habeas corpus, granted to the extent of directing that petitioner be given a final parole revocation hearing at the next regular term of the board. Gulotta, P. J., Rabin, Hopkins, Martuscello and Latham, JJ., concur.
